<p>27 August 2020 <br />
<em><a href="https://www.csa.iisc.ac.in/~chiru/">Prof.Chiranjib Bhattacharyya</a> takes charge as the Chair of CSA Department</em></p>

<p>9 January 2020 <br />
<em><a href="https://www.csa.iisc.ac.in/~chiru/">Prof.Chiranjib Bhattacharyya</a> is organising <a href="https://www.csa.iisc.ac.in/fate.htm#links"> FATE ML workshop </a>. This workshop on Fairness, Accountability, Transparency and Ethics in Machine Learning is organised in collaboration with <a href="https://www.iisc.ac.in/">IISc</a>, <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/linkedin/"> LinkedIn</a> and <a href="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/">Microsoft Research</a></em></p>

<p>9 January 2020 <br />
<em>Paper titled ‘Finding a latent k–simplex in O* (k·nnz(data)) time via Subset Smoothing’ by <a href="https://www.csa.iisc.ac.in/~chiru/">Prof.Chiranjib Bhattacharyya</a> and <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ravindran_Kannan">Ravindran Kannan</a> published in SODA</em></p>

